1
00:00:00,809 --> 00:00:03,029
You just connected with me now,
didn't you?

2
00:00:03,819 --> 00:00:05,059
You can see visions.

3
00:00:08,860 --> 00:00:09,860
Relax.

4
00:00:10,120 --> 00:00:12,820
Although I guess that's easier said than
done.

5
00:00:13,833 --> 00:00:14,893
Are you alright?

6
00:00:15,799 --> 00:00:18,246
I... I just got shot,
but... 

7
00:00:18,703 --> 00:00:19,609
I understand.

8
00:00:19,960 --> 00:00:21,280
Listen, you have to come with me.

9
00:00:23,366 --> 00:00:24,673
You're not safe here.

10
00:00:27,506 --> 00:00:28,506
Follow me.

